# Tor configuration for Nimble Node.
#
# The tor container shares the lit container's network namespace
# (network_mode: "service:lit"), so LND reaches the SOCKS and control ports on
# 127.0.0.1 and Tor reaches LND's p2p listener on 127.0.0.1:9735. LND creates
# and manages its own v3 onion service through the control port.
#
# Authentication uses the control cookie (the standard method): Tor writes it
# to DataDirectory, and the lit container reads it via the shared tor-data
# volume mounted at the same path.

SocksPort 127.0.0.1:9050
ControlPort 127.0.0.1:9051
CookieAuthentication 1
CookieAuthFileGroupReadable 1
DataDirectory /var/lib/tor
Log notice stdout
